  "texts": [
    "There was no indication of multicollinearity issues as VIF values were below five.",
    "In addition, the predictive relevance of the proposed model was reinforced as Q 2 coefficient values were greater than zero (Kock, 2022b).",
    "The hypotheses were examined using the results of the structural model.",
    "Table 4 summarizes the results of the structural model assessment: path coefficients (β, path significance (p-value), and effect sizes (f²).",
    "f² values of 0.35, 0.15, and 0.02 indicate large, medium, and small effect sizes, respectively (Cohen, 1988)."
  ]
